---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<Layout 
  title="Lead-to-CRM Automation | LogicLoom Systems"
  description="Instant sync from Facebook/Typeform to HubSpot. Call leads in under 60 seconds."
>
  <div>
    
    <section class="pt-40 pb-20 px-6 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-8 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-indigo-200 bg-indigo-50/60 text-indigo-700">
        <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></span>
        <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Workflow: Sales Ops</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
        From "New Lead" to <br /> "Hello" in <span class="text-indigo-600">2 Seconds.</span>
      </h1>
 
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Stop manually copying leads from Facebook Ads or Typeform. We build pipelines that inject leads into your CRM instantly and alert your sales team via Slack.
      </p>
      <button @click="$dispatch('open-modal')" class="bg-indigo-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-indigo-500/20 cursor-pointer">
        Automate My Pipeline
      </button>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-white border-y border-gray-100">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold mb-6">The "Cold Lead" Problem</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              If you wait 5 minutes to call a lead, your odds of qualifying them drop by 80%. If you're manually exporting CSVs from Facebook Ads at the end of the day, those leads are already dead.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 mt-8">
            <li class="flex gap-3 items-start"><Icon name="ph:x-circle" class="text-red-500 mt-1" /> <span class="text-gray-600">Manual data entry errors (typos in phone numbers).</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3 items-start"><Icon name="ph:x-circle" class="text-red-500 mt-1" /> <span class="text-gray-600">Sales team doesn't know a lead came in.</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3 items-start"><Icon name="ph:x-circle" class="text-red-500 mt-1" /> <span class="text-gray-600">No immediate "Thank You" SMS sent.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white p-8 rounded-2xl font-mono text-sm shadow-2xl">
          <div class="text-green-400 mb-4">// LogicLoom Lead Pipeline</div>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-center p-3 bg-white/5 rounded border border-white/10">
              <Icon name="ph:facebook-logo" class="text-blue-400 text-xl" />
              <div>
                <div class="font-bold">New Lead Received</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">Trigger: Facebook Ad Form</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-center"><Icon name="ph:arrow-down" class="text-gray-500" /></div>
           
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-center p-3 bg-white/5 rounded border border-white/10">
              <Icon name="ph:lightning" class="text-orange-400 text-xl" />
              <div>
                <div class="font-bold">n8n Formatting</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">Format Phone (+1) & Validate Email</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-center"><Icon name="ph:arrow-down" class="text-gray-500" /></div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-center p-3 bg-white/5 rounded border border-white/10">
              <Icon name="ph:slack-logo" class="text-purple-400 text-xl" />
              <div>
                <div class="font-bold">Slack Alert + CRM Sync</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">Sales team tagged instantly.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

<section class="py-24 bg-indigo-50 border-t border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
    
    <div>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-800">
            <Icon name="ph:bell-ringing" />
            <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Instant Notification</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Leads rot in CSVs.<br/>They convert in Slack.</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
            The moment a prospect hits "Submit" on your Facebook Ad, your sales team gets a ping. No refreshing the CRM. No waiting for the daily export.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 border border-indigo-100 mt-1">
                    <Icon name="ph:users-three" />
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Round-Robin Assignment</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">The system auto-assigns the lead to the next available rep.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
    
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 border border-indigo-100 mt-1">
                    <Icon name="ph:phone-call" />
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900">One-Click Dialing</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">The Slack alert includes a tel:// link. Reps click and talk instantly.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-2xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden max-w-md mx-auto transform rotate-1 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500">
        <div class="bg-[#350d36] px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                 <span class="opacity-70">#</span> inbound-leads
            </div>
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded bg-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white shrink-0">
                    <Icon name="ph:robot" class="text-xl" />
                </div>
                <div class="w-full">
                    <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-1">
                        <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm">LogicLoom Bot</span>
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">APP</span>
                        <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">10:42 AM</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-green-500 pl-3 mt-1">
                        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-green-700 mb-1">ðŸ”¥ New High-Value Lead</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-800 mb-3"><strong>John Smith</strong> just submitted the "Q4 Pricing" form on Facebook.</p>
          
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-y-2 text-xs text-gray-600 mb-4 bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded">
                            <span class="font-bold">Email:</span> <span>john@company.com</span>
                            <span class="font-bold">Company:</span> <span>TechCorp Inc.</span>
                            <span class="font-bold">Budget:</span> <span>$10k - $25k</span>
                            <span class="font-bold">Source:</span> <span>FB_Campaign_v2</span>
                        </div>

                         <div class="flex gap-2">
                            <button class="bg-green-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-2 rounded hover:bg-green-700 w-full">
                                ðŸ“ž Call Now
                            </button>
                            <button class="bg-white border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-2 rounded hover:bg-gray-50 w-full">
                                View in HubSpot
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-24 bg-slate-900 text-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold mb-4">The "Clean Data" Pipeline</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400">We don't just sync leads. We validate, format, and enrich them first.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative">
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 via-indigo-500 to-purple-500 transform -translate-y-1/2 opacity-30"></div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 relative z-10">
        
        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-400 transition-all text-center group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto bg-slate-900 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center border border-slate-700 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-blue-400">
            <Icon name="ph:funnel" class="text-2xl" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">1. Ingest</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Catches webhooks from Typeform, Facebook, LinkedIn, or Website.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 hover:border-indigo-400 transition-all text-center group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto bg-slate-900 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center border border-slate-700 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-indigo-400">
            <Icon name="ph:magic-wand" class="text-2xl" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">2. Format</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Capitalizes names. Formats phone numbers (E.164). Validates email syntax.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 hover:border-purple-400 transition-all text-center group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto bg-slate-900 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center border border-slate-700 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-purple-400">
            <Icon name="ph:copy" class="text-2xl" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">3. Dedupe</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Checks CRM for existing email. If found, updates the record. If new, creates one.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 hover:border-green-400 transition-all text-center group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto bg-slate-900 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center border border-slate-700 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-green-400">
            <Icon name="ph:rocket-launch" class="text-2xl" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">4. Alert</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Pushes high-priority leads to Slack and enrolls them in email drip sequences.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center text-slate-900">FAQ</h2>
    
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div x-data="{ open: false }" class="bg-slate-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <button @click="open = !open" class="flex justify-between items-center w-full p-4 text-left font-bold text-slate-900 hover:bg-gray-100">
          <span>Does this create duplicate contacts?</span>
          <Icon name="ph:caret-down" class="text-gray-500" />
        </button>
        <div x-show="open" class="p-4 pt-0 text-gray-600 text-sm">
          No. Our n8n workflow always performs a "Search" step first. If a contact exists with that email, we update their record with the new form data. We only create a new contact if no match is found.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div x-data="{ open: false }" class="bg-slate-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <button @click="open = !open" class="flex justify-between items-center w-full p-4 text-left font-bold text-slate-900 hover:bg-gray-100">
          <span>Can we filter out bad leads (e.g., Gmail addresses)?</span>
          <Icon name="ph:caret-down" class="text-gray-500" />
        </button>
        <div x-show="open" class="p-4 pt-0 text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Yes. We can add a "Filter" node that checks if the email domain is `@gmail.com` or `@yahoo.com`. If it is, we can route it to a different list or skip the Slack alert entirely.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div x-data="{ open: false }" class="bg-slate-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <button @click="open = !open" class="flex justify-between items-center w-full p-4 text-left font-bold text-slate-900 hover:bg-gray-100">
          <span>What CRMs do you support?</span>
          <Icon name="ph:caret-down" class="text-gray-500" />
        </button>
        <div x-show="open" class="p-4 pt-0 text-gray-600 text-sm">
          We have native support for HubSpot, Salesforce, Pipedrive, Zoho, and HighLevel. If your CRM has an API or Webhook support, we can connect to it.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

    </div>
</Layout>